The Green Knight story encodes a pattern that appears everywhere:

Domain	Example
ecology	killing predators causes ecosystem collapse
economics	suppressing volatility creates bigger crashes
psychology	repressing problems makes them return stronger
geopolitics	unresolved conflicts reappear decades later

The Green Knight is basically a mythological model of feedback loops.

